sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor DO as Data Owner / SME
  participant PA as Power Automate
  participant SP as SharePoint Site
  participant KB as Excel/SharePoint list <br> Knowledge Base

  PA->>SP: Monitor KB (schedule / trigger)
  PA-->>DO: Reminder to review or update data
  DO->>SP: Update Excel/SharePoint list content
  SP->>KB: Save latest version
  PA->>SP: Validate freshness / completeness

  alt Outdated / missing info detected
    PA-->>DO: Warning / escalation notification
  else Up to date
    PA-->>DO: Confirmation / no action needed
  end